title: North Korea tests medium-range missile fuelling fears over its ability to hit US

author: FOCUS Online
description: Drei Monate Ferien auf Hawaii – davon träumen viele Urlauber. Eine Australierin wollte sich diesen Wunsch erfüllen. Doch amerikanische Grenzbeamte verhafteten die junge Frau am Flughafen – wegen ihrer privaten Notizen.
title: Gefängnis statt Urlaub: US-Grenzbeamte verhaften junge Frau wegen ihres Tagebuchs

author: MICHAEL BALSAMO
description: LOS ANGELES (AP) — A man acted strangely long before he caused a disturbance on a plane that prompted fighter jets to accompany it to Hawaii, but a lack of communication and an airline's hesitancy to be caught on video booting a passenger could have played a role in allowing him to fly, experts say. Anil Uskanli, 25, of Turkey, had purchased a ticket at an airline counter in the middle of the night with no luggage and had been arrested after opening a door to a restricted airfield at Los Angeles International Airport. Airport police did not notify the airline, but they said it isn't common practice.
title: Experts: Lack of communication before plane disturbance
